\begin_layout Standard
设 
\begin_inset Formula $k\in(0,1)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $E(k)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $F(k)$
\end_inset

 分别为第二类与第一类完全椭圆积分 (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:ellE-2"
